Synopsis: 
The Autobots Bumblebee, Ratchet, Ironhide and Sideswipe, led by Optimus Prime, return to action, confronting the evil Decepticons, who are determined to settle scores for his defeat of 2009 in 'Transformers 2: Revenge of the Fallen'. In this new movie the Autobots and Decepticons are involved in the dangerous space race between the United States and Russia, and once more Sam Witwicky the human need to come to the rescue of his friends robots. There are also new characters, including a new villain takes the form of Shockwave, and an old acquaintance of the Transformers Cybertron that reigns while fighting the Autobots and Decepticons on Earth. 

Production notes: 
Third installment of the saga "Transformers" (2007) and 'Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen' (2009)
